<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>Facility Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #4a4a4a;
        background-color: #f0f4f9;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: auto;
        background-color: #fff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        border-top: 4px solid #4caf50;
      }
      a,
      a:visited {
        color: #4caf50;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:hover,
      a:active {
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .header {
        color: #fff;
        background-color: #4caf50;
        padding: 10px;
        border-radius: 4px 4px 0 0;
        font-size: 24px;
        line-height: 28px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .footer {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #909090;
        margin-top: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body style="background-color: #f0f4f9">
    <br><br>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">Facility Booking Request Received</div>
      <h4>Dear <%= firstname %> <%= lastname %>,</h4>
      <p>
        We have successfully received your request for facility booking. Here
        are the details you provided:
      </p>
      <table style="margin: auto; width: 90%; text-align: left">
        
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Facility:</strong></td>
          <td><%= facility.category %> <%= facility.name %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Location:</strong></td>
          <td><%= facility.location %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>Start Period:</strong></td>
          <td><%= startPeriod %></td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td><strong>End Period:</strong></td>
          <td><%= endPeriod %></td>
        </tr>
      </table>
      <p>
        Your request is currently being processed, and we will notify you as
        soon as your booking is confirmed.
      </p>
      <p>
        Should you have any additional requests or questions, please do not
        hesitate to reach out by replying to this email or contacting us at
        <a href="mailto:email@example.com">email@example.com</a>.
      </p>
      <p>Thank you for choosing our booking service!</p>
      <p>Warm regards,<br />UR Digitalization Services</p>
      <div class="footer">
        This is an automated message, please do not reply directly. <br />
        For further assistance, reply to this email or reach out through the
        appropriate channels.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
